    http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4

    ValueWithAttributes TimeSpan

      • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4:TimeSpan

      • Description

        Specifies the arrival date and departure date which covers the whole Reservation.

    • Example XML

      <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>

<TimeSpan end="2016-08-28T04:32:52Z" start="2016-08-22T19:32:52Z" xmlns="http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4"/>

      Example JSON

      {
  "TimeSpan" : {
    "value" : null,
    "start" : "2016-08-22T19:32:52Z",
    "end" : "2016-08-28T04:32:52Z"
  }
}

      • Attribute Summary

        Attributes 
        Name Description
        start
        Specifies the start date for the booking as a whole.
        Details
        Type DateTime
        Example Value 2016-08-22T19:32:52Z
        Required true
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        end
        Specifies the end date for the booking as a whole.
        Details
        Type DateTime
        Example Value 2016-08-28T04:32:52Z
        Required true
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
